    "description": "Sahyadri Hospitals Global Group, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Surgeon for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sahyadri Hospitals Global Group:\nSahyadri Hospitals Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain sterile environments and follow infection control protocols\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sahyadri Hospitals Global Group!",
